To plot indicator values, in the OnData event handler, call the Plot method.

private RateOfChangeRatio _rocr;

// In Initialize()
var symbol = AddEquity("SPY").Symbol;
_rocr = ROCR(symbol, period);

// In OnData()
if (_rocr.IsReady)
{
    Plot("My Indicators", "rateofchangeratio", _rocr.Current.Value);
}
